headline: Weyerhaeuser Appoints Paul Hossain as Senior Vice President and Chief Development Officer
summary: Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE: WY) today announced the appointment of Paul Hossain as senior vice president and chief development officer, effective January 1, 2025. In this role, he will oversee the company's Real Estate, Energy & Natural Resources segment, including its Natural Climate Solutions business, as well as Business Development and Acquisitions and Divestitures.
